<!-- ════════════════ 22 · STAP 3 — AI CAPABILITY MAP ════════════════ -->
  <section data-label="Stap 3 — Map" class="slide light">
    <div class="glow"></div>
    <div class="frame">
      <div class="step-strip">
        <span class="pill">Stap 1</span>
        <span class="pill">Stap 2</span>
        <span class="sep">→</span>
        <span class="pill on">Stap 3 · AI capability map</span>
        <span class="pill">Stap 4</span>
        <span class="pill">Stap 5</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="title" style="max-width: 1500px; font-size: 64px;">Welke capabilities brengt AI mee — en waar<br>maak je bewuste keuzes tussen <span class="accent">mens en AI</span>?</h1>

      <div class="grid-2-side" style="margin-top: 32px; align-items: center;">
        <p class="body" style="font-size: 26px; max-width: 760px;">
          Elke job to be done vraagt capabilities. Sommige liggen bij mensen, andere bij technologie, en steeds meer in een overlapzone. Daar — in dat strategisch spanningsveld — maak je de keuzes die je organisatie typeren.
          <br><br>
          <span style="color: var(--fg);">Een veelgemaakte fout: aannemen dat AI "de job" overneemt, terwijl het in werkelijkheid maar een deel van de nodige capabilities invult.</span>
          <br><br>
          <span style="font-style: italic; color: var(--sa-cyan);">"Het is niet omdat het kan, dat het ook een goed idee is." — SmartAgents</span>
        </p>

        <!-- Venn diagram -->
        <div class="chart-card" style="position: relative; max-width: 580px; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; padding: 20px;">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 720 600" width="100%" height="100%">
            <!-- AI circle -->
            <circle cx="260" cy="320" r="220" fill="#00d8ff" fill-opacity="0.16" stroke="#00d8ff" stroke-width="2"/>
            <!-- Human circle -->
            <circle cx="460" cy="320" r="220" fill="#0891b2" fill-opacity="0.14" stroke="#0891b2" stroke-width="2"/>
            <!-- Labels -->
            <text x="100" y="160" fill="#00d8ff" font-size="24" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter" letter-spacing="2">AI</text>
            <text x="620" y="160" fill="#0891b2" font-size="24" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter" letter-spacing="2" text-anchor="end">MENS</text>

            <text x="170" y="320" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fff" font-size="24" font-weight="600" font-family="Inter">AI-zone</text>
            <text x="170" y="350" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.65)" font-size="24" font-family="Inter">bewust AI</text>

            <text x="550" y="320" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fff" font-size="24" font-weight="600" font-family="Inter">Menselijke zone</text>
            <text x="550" y="350" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.65)" font-size="24" font-family="Inter">bewust mens</text>

            <text x="360" y="310" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fff" font-size="24" font-weight="700" font-family="Inter">Spanningsveld</text>
            <text x="360" y="340" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.85)" font-size="24" font-family="Inter">mens ↔ AI</text>

            <text x="360" y="580" text-anchor="middle" fill="#00d8ff" font-size="24" font-weight="600" font-family="Inter" letter-spacing="3">OVERLAP = STRATEGISCHE KEUZE</text>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% set slideNumber = "22" %}
    {% set slideTotal = "29" %}
    {% include "../../shared/chrome.njk" %}
  </section>
